Package client.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClientModel
    Contains all data relevant to the game
    ClientModelController
    Handles all "CanDo" methods and provides access to the client model
    DevCardList
    Stores the different types of development cards
    Hex
    Represents a map hex, stores its location, what resource it represents, and its number to be rolled
    Map
    Represents the game map, stores relevant locations and layout
    MessageLine
    One line of a message with the name of the player who sent it
    MessageList
    A list of lines that make up a message
    Player
    Represents a player in the game, contains relevant data, cards held, etc.
    Port
    The port hex, contains location and trading ratio
    ResourceList
    A list of resources
    Road
    Contains the location and owner of a Road, changed from EdgeValue in the specs, because that was a poor name.
    TradeOffer
    Contains the contents of a trade offer, the sender, receiver, and resources.
    TurnTracker
    Tracks the current turn as well as longest road/army awards
    VertexObject
    An object placed on a vertex, city or settlement
